# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
# confucian.ese — 儒家词库 / Confucian Vocabulary
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════
#
# 四书五经 as standard library.
# The Five Constant Virtues (五常) as fundamental operations:
#   仁 (Rén)  — Benevolence  → DISTRIBUTE (share resources)
#   义 (Yì)   — Righteousness → VALIDATE (verify correctness)
#   礼 (Lǐ)   — Ritual        → ORCHESTRATE (coordinate processes)
#   智 (Zhì)  — Wisdom        → OPTIMIZE (find best solution)
#   信 (Xìn)  — Trust         → VERIFY (ensure integrity)
#
# These map to core programming concepts:
#   Distribution = parallelism / fan-out
#   Validation = type checking / assertions
#   Orchestration = workflow / sequencing
#   Optimization = compilation / efficiency
#   Verification = testing / integrity checks
#
# ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

# ── Domain declaration ──────────────────────────────────────
@domain: 儒 (confucian)
@description: 四书五经标准词库 — 儒家概念映射为程序操作

# ── Operations (五常 → 五运算) ─────────────────────────────
仁 → DISTRIBUTE   # Benevolence: fan-out, distribute to all
义 → VALIDATE     # Righteousness: assert, verify correctness
礼 → ORCHESTRATE  # Ritual: sequence, coordinate workflow
智 → OPTIMIZE     # Wisdom: find optimal solution
信 → VERIFY       # Trust: cryptographic verification, integrity

# ── Extended Confucian concepts ─────────────────────────────
德 → INTEGRITY    # Virtue: system integrity
道 → PRINCIPLE    # Way: architectural principle
理 → LOGIC        # Reason: logical operation
气 → ENERGY       # Qi: system resource / throughput
阴阳 → BALANCE    # Yin-Yang: load balancing
中庸 → MODERATE   # Golden Mean: rate limiting
天人 → WHOLE      # Heaven-Human unity: system holistic view

# ── Social hierarchy → process hierarchy ────────────────────
君 → SUPERVISOR   # Ruler: supervisory process
臣 → WORKER       # Minister: worker process
民 → DATA         # People: data / payload
邦 → NAMESPACE    # State: namespace / module

# ── Learning → compilation ─────────────────────────────────
学 → COMPILE      # Learning: compile / transform
思 → ANALYZE      # Thinking: static analysis
习 → EXECUTE      # Practice: runtime execution
问 → ASK          # Inquiring: query external agent

# ── Analects patterns ──────────────────────────────────────
# 学而时习之 → COMPILE then EXECUTE on schedule
# 温故而知新 → REPLAY history, DISCOVER new patterns
# 三人行必有我师 → POLL 3 agents, SELECT best response
